name: Watching My Creations: 1k Dreamz
description:
Thank you to everyone who has been so embracing of me and my art in the HEN and NFT space. My artist community gives me life and I wanted to say thank you! This is a present celebrating 1k followers in the NFT Twitter Space.

World was hand drawn in Virtual Reality and altered/textured in Blender. I used Resolume's camera to enter the clip and interact with my world. Join me!
